Package: MedianaADT
Type: Package
Title: Adaptive design toolkit
Version: 0.1
Date: 2020-11-25
Author: Alex Dmitrienko
Depends: R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.10), officer, flextable, devEMF, shiny, shinydashboard, shinyMatrix
Suggests: testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Maintainer: Alex Dmitrienko <admitrienko@medianainc.com>
Description: 
    Adaptive design kit with five modules: 
    Module A (Adaptive designs with data-driven sample size or event count re-estimation), 
    Module B (Adaptive designs with data-driven treatment selection), 
    Module C (Adaptive designs with data-driven population selection), 
    Module D (Optimal selection of a futility stopping rule), 
    Module E (Event prediction in event-driven trials).
License: GPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: true
NeedsCompilation: yes
Packaged: 2020-11-25
Repository: CRAN
Date/Publication: 2020-11-11
